HEADWORD: Unanswerable
<hw>Un*an"swer*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
answerable; irrefutable; conclusive; decisive; <as>as, he gave an
<ex>unanswerable</ex> argument</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*an"swer*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Un*an"swer*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

